{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "常笑带官差夜访宋妈妈住所，逼问魔药真相。宋妈妈吞下魔药后诅咒常笑，常笑毫不畏惧，一剑刺死宋妈妈。王风在墙上发现血奴鸟图案的活壁，揭开魔画之谜。常笑下令搜查，唐老大发现祭坛黑鼎烟雾有毒，警告众人口已遭董昌斩杀。十个官差在毒雾中发疯自相残杀，常笑趁机夺取解毒药丸保命。王风中毒发狂，追杀常笑至门外。常笑逃脱后，王风在乱葬岗毒发倒地，神秘幽灵出现喂下药丸。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你就是宋妈妈？",
      "tone": "冷声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "听说你是个巫婆？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你这间房子据说亦是与众不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "其实没有多大不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "我很想参观一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "我这里没有什么值得参观。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你不欢迎我参观？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你好像知道那是什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "有人跟我说过这种魇药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "魔药？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "据说是用粪便、月经、眼泪和脓血混合面粉之后做成的东西，吃了后就可以跟妖魔沟通。",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "有人肯吃这种东西？",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "最低限度这里就有一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "是不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "活见鬼，我宁可拿刀子抹脖子。",
      "tone": "恶心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那是宋妈妈了？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "吃过魔药之后据说她的诅咒就会很灵验，所以这地方很多人都怕她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "她莫非也诅咒过你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "所以我才有机会见她将那种魔药放入口中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "那种东西真的是魔药？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "真的用粪便、月经、眼泪、脓血再混合面粉来做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "还有尿液。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你真的敢吃那种东西吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "当然是真的，只是不常吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "那种东西也是你做的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "除了我没有其他人做那种东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "用你自己的粪便、月经、眼泪、尿液、脓血？",
      "tone": "厌恶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "当然都得用我自己的东西，否则，我吃了下去，也是没有作用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你还有月经？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你好像忘了自己有多大年纪？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "看来这个巫婆要诅咒你了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "只不知她的诅咒灵验，还是我的剑灵验。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "你这个巫婆最好就赶快将那块魔药吐出来。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人的嘴巴，一定会被割掉，这个人的双手，一定会被斩下，这个人的心肝，一定会被挖出来喂狗……",
      "tone": "诅咒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "这个人如果再说下去，她的咽喉之上立即会多出一个血洞。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "这个人尽管住了口，她的咽喉很快还是会多出一个血洞。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "据讲只有死亡才能制止诅咒的存在，为了自己的嘴巴不被割掉，双手不被斩下，心肝不被挖出来喂狗，我只有赶快杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "天咒你，咒你下地狱，上……上刀山……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "text": "也咒你死在我的剑下。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还以为真的魔鸟作祟，原来是这方活壁作怪。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我早说过这个地方也许有些东西能够解开你心中的疑团。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这个地方一直在黑暗之中，什么颜色的东西在黑暗之中看来都是一样，所以他们才会疏忽了，其实在你刷掉的魔画之后，他们就应该将这方活壁也削成漆黑，那即使我在这里大放光明，亦未必可以发现这个秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "也许他们真的疏忽了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "听你说到魔鸟的笑声，我就已怀疑这面墙壁，那笑声怕不是出自宋妈妈的口中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_chang_xiao",
      "text": "问问她就清楚了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你可以问另外一个人的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要不是真的疏忽，他们可能因为有更多，更重要的事情需要打点，无暇兼顾，这房子之内，莫非还有什么古怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们给我搜！彻底搜！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "唐老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雾中有毒！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    }
  ],
